    ],
    "text": "South-West monsoon is gradually getting established over the island. Showers will occur at times in Western, Sabaragamuwa and North-western provinces and in Galle, Matara, Kandy and Nuwara-Eliya districts. Fairly heavy falls above 50 mm are likely at some places in the above areas.",
