      61.34,
      504.34,
      557.8,
      539.23
    ],
    "text": "The wave height may increase (about 2.0 - 2.5m) in the sea areas off the coast extending from Mannar to Pottuvil via Puttalam, Colombo, Galle and Hambantota (this is not for land area).",
